Determine the output of the following code.

```java
public class Box {
    private int value;

    public Box(int v) { value = v; }
    public int getValue() { return value; }
    public void setValue(int v) { value = v; }
}

public static void change(Box b, int n) {
    b.setValue(n);
    b = new Box(99);
}

Box myBox = new Box(10);
change(myBox, 50);
System.out.println(myBox.getValue());
```

