```java
public class Point
{
    private int x;
    private int y;

    public Point(int x, int y)
    {
        this.x = x;
        this.y = y;
    }

    public void shift(int x, int y)
    {
        x = this.x + x;
        y = this.y + y;
    }

    public int getX() { return x; }
    public int getY() { return y; }
}
```

```java
Point p = new Point(3, 4);
p.shift(2, 5);
