Consider the following class.

```java
public class Ticket {
    private static int nextId = 1;
    private int id;
    private String event;

    public Ticket(String event) {
        this.event = event;
        id = nextId;
        nextId++;
    }

    public int getId() { return id; }
}
```

What is printed after the following code executes?

```java
